---
// src/pages/accessibility.astro
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility"
  description="Accessibility statement for Chris Collier's IT portfolio."
>
  <div class="accessibility-page">
    <div class="container py-5">
      <div class="page-header mb-5">
        <p class="prompt mb-1">
          <span class="prompt-user">chris@portfolio</span><span
            class="prompt-sep">:</span
          ><span class="prompt-path">~</span><span class="prompt-sep">$</span>
          <span class="prompt-cmd"> cat ./accessibility.txt</span>
        </p>
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-white">Accessibility Statement</h1>
        <div class="header-line mt-2"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <p class="body-text">
          This portfolio is built with accessibility as a core requirement, not
          an afterthought. It is designed to meet <strong class="text-light"
            >WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong
          > standards.
        </p>

        <h2 class="section-title mt-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Skip to main content</strong> — a keyboard-accessible
            link appears at the top of every page, allowing screen reader and keyboard
            users to bypass navigation.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Keyboard navigation</strong> — all interactive
            elements are reachable and operable via keyboard. Focus indicators are
            clearly visible on every focusable element.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Text resizer</strong> — a floating control
            in the bottom-right corner allows text size to be adjusted to small, medium,
            or large. Your preference is saved for future visits.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Screen reader support</strong> — semantic HTML,
            ARIA labels, and descriptive alt text are used throughout. Decorative
            icons are hidden from assistive technology.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Colour contrast</strong> — all text meets or
            exceeds WCAG AA contrast ratio requirements against their backgrounds.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">Responsive design</strong> — the site is fully
            functional across all screen sizes and devices.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="feature-icon">▸</span>
            <strong class="text-light">No auto-playing media</strong> — no audio or
            video plays automatically.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="section-title mt-4">Known Limitations</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          This site is actively maintained. If you encounter any accessibility
          barriers not listed here, please get in touch.
        </p>

        <h2 class="section-title mt-4">Feedback</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          If you experience any difficulty accessing content on this site,
          please contact me via
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-collier-tech/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-link">LinkedIn</a
          >. I aim to respond within 2 business days.
        </p>

        <h2 class="section-title mt-4">Technical Specification</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          Built with <strong class="text-light">Astro</strong> and <strong
            class="text-light">Bootstrap 5.3</strong
          >. Tested with keyboard-only navigation and VoiceOver (macOS). Last
          reviewed: May 2026.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .accessibility-page {
    background-color: #0f1117;
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .page-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2533;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prompt {
    font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .prompt-user {
    color: #68d391;
  }
  .prompt-sep {
    color: #a0aec0;
  }
  .prompt-path {
    color: #63b3ed;
  }
  .prompt-cmd {
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .header-line {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #68d391;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .content-card {
    background: #1a1f2e;
    border: 1px solid #2d3748;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #68d391;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2d3748;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .body-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #a0aec0;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #a0aec0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: #68d391;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .text-link {
    color: #90cdf4;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .text-link:hover {
    color: #68d391;
  }
</style>
